---
// Artist manifesto section
---

<section id="manifesto" class="relative py-32 bg-ink text-paper overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <!-- Diagonal stripes -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 35px, #FF006E 35px, #FF006E 70px);"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="font-graffiti text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl mb-4">
        <span class="glitch" data-text="THE MANIFESTO">THE MANIFESTO</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="font-mono text-punk uppercase tracking-widest">
        Why I'm not your typical bookkeeper
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Manifesto content in magazine layout -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20">
      <!-- Left column -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-8 top-0 font-graffiti text-8xl text-punk/20">01</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-electric">
            I'M AN ARTIST TOO
          </h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Started as a painter. Got tired of eating ramen. Learned bookkeeping. 
            Now I eat sushi AND help artists do the same.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-8 top-0 font-graffiti text-8xl text-punk/20">02</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-acid">
            YOUR MESS IS MY MUSE
          </h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Shoebox full of receipts? Bank statements covered in paint? 
            Three years of "I'll do it tomorrow"? That's not chaos. 
            That's Tuesday for me.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-8 top-0 font-graffiti text-8xl text-punk/20">03</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-violet">
            NO CORPORATE BULLSH*T
          </h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-lg leading-relaxed">
            I won't make you wear a suit. I won't judge your 
            "creative accounting." I will make sure you're legal, 
            profitable, and can afford better paint.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right column -->
      <div class="space-y-8 md:mt-20">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-8 top-0 font-graffiti text-8xl text-punk/20">04</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-punk">
            I SPEAK YOUR LANGUAGE
          </h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Commission? Grant? Gallery cut? Barter deal? 
            I know the difference and how to track it all. 
            Your CPA will think you hired a Fortune 500 accountant.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-8 top-0 font-graffiti text-8xl text-punk/20">05</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-electric">
            DEDUCTIONS ARE MY DRUG
          </h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-lg leading-relaxed">
            That vintage frame? Write-off. Studio playlist subscription? 
            Deductible. Trip to MoMA? Research, baby. I find money 
            where other bookkeepers see receipts.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -left-8 top-0 font-graffiti text-8xl text-punk/20">06</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-acid">
            YOUR SUCCESS = MY ART
          </h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-lg leading-relaxed">
            When you can afford a bigger studio, better supplies, 
            or that residency in Iceland - that's my masterpiece. 
            Your financial freedom is my gallery opening.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-20">
      <div class="inline-block relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-electric via-punk to-acid blur-xl opacity-50"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-ink border-4 border-paper px-12 py-6">
          <p class="font-graffiti text-3xl mb-2">READY TO BURN THE RULEBOOK?</p>
          <p class="font-mono text-lg text-punk">(While staying 100% IRS compliant)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>